data.title: Angel Martinez (Baseball Player) - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Angel Martinez (Baseball Player): his birthday, what he did before fame, his family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Professional second baseman and middle infielder that was first signed by the Cleveland Guardians as an international free agent in 2018. A few years later, he was named the tenth-best MLB prospect in Cleveland's farm system. In November of 2022, the Guardians selected his contract from the Akron Rubber Ducks.

Before Fame

He originally began his professional career playing for the DSL Indians. He was only a teenager at the time of his professional debut.

Trivia

He recorded a career-high 101 hits during the 2022 minor league season. In addition, he also recorded career highs in home runs, walks, and doubles.

Family Life

He grew up living with his family in Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic. He is the son of Sandy Martinez.
